      "paragraphs": [
        "Angle + curve/geometry math helpers, grouped as a namespace. The common scalar utilities (`clamp`, `lerp`, `sign`, `inRange`, `isPowerOfTwo`, `TAU`) are free top-level exports instead — see `src/math/index.ts`. This facade groups the less-common angle/curve/geometry helpers that don't warrant their own top-level export."
